    "summary": "Time to shift to higher gear and scale your business ? A highly intelligent and innovative business developer with proven success and 20+ years of leading teams in product management, marketing, sales and innovation. I like to help companies grow business by implementing innovative technologies with customer impact.    Feel free to connect via LinkedIn or contact me directly at huub.appelboom@kpnmail.nl\n\nSTRATEGIC PRODUCT MARKETING EXECUTIVE\nBusiness Development | Product Management | Innovation\n\nAdded Value\n- Unique combination of commercial and high-tech experience and expertise, and a proven success record in scaling business.\n- Well-versed in understanding customer needs and conversion into products.\n- Creates and improves business policies and methodologies for innovation and business growth.\n\nTrack record\n- More than 20 years experience of managing cross-functional teams to achieve strategic, business, sales, marketing and engineering objectives. \n- International and domestic work experience in fast paced, high profile organizations. \n\nAchievements\n- Built mobile internet revenue from zero to +200 million Euro in 8 years.\n- Achieved year-on-year triple digit growth rates.\n- Winner of KPN Board Award for outstanding achievements.\n\nSkills and Interests\nExceptional analytical, communication, interpersonal and cross-functional collaboration skills. Possess acute strategic acumen. Instrumental in product innovations, enhancing productivity, improving business processes and sales, and implementing technology solutions. Product management, innovation, product strategy and positioning, marketing communication, sales, digital strategy formulation, business building, planning & leadership, contract negotiations, pricing, digital transformation, implementing disruptive technologies, engineering, mobile, internet, artificial intelligence, data, social media, online content, campaigning and platforms, user experience, market and customer research, internet of things, cyber security, privacy, electronic identities, business administration; stakeholder relationship management; organization and business transformation; consultative services and overall business innovation. \n\nGet in touch with me\nReady to scale your business ?  Please get in touch with me on LinkedIn, in order to find out if we can be of value to each other. Also, feel free to connect with me and personalize your invitation.\n\nHuub Appelboom\nTelephone +31 653368371\nEmail huub.appelboom@kpnmail.nl\n\nHave a nice day !",
